dataformat.name: any23
dataformat.title: Any23
dataformat.description: Extract RDF data from HTML documents.
dataformat.label: dataformat,transformation

outputFormat.description: What RDF syntax to unmarshal as, can be: NTRIPLES, TURTLE, NQUADS, RDFXML, JSONLD, RDFJSON, RDF4JMODEL. It is by default: RDF4JMODEL.

baseUri.description: The URI to use as base for building RDF entities if only relative paths are provided.

configuration.description: Configurations for Apache Any23 as key-value pairs in order to customize the extraction process. The list of supported parameters can be found here. If not provided, a default configuration is used.

extractors.description: List of Any23 extractors to be used in the unmarshal operation. A list of the available extractors can be found here here. If not provided, all the available extractors are used.
